<div id="narrow_container">
  <h1>Where are my taxes going?</h1>
  <h2>For the first time in history, Australian citizens can finally see where the government spends their money.<br/>TheOpenBudget is a new government expenditure dataset and visualisation tool to examine what money goes where. </h2>

  <div id="chart">
  </div>
  <div id="sidebar">
    <div class="option">
      <div class="title">
        Select a Financial Year:
      </div>
      <button class='first active year_toggle' id='12_13'>
        12-13 Budget
      </button>
      <button class='last year_toggle' id='11_12'>
        11-12 Actual
      </button>
    </div>
    <div class="item_detail">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="label">Name:</div>
        <div id="item_name" class="value"></div>
        <div class="clear"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="label">Cost to the average taxpayer:</div>
        <div id="individual_taxpayer" class="value"></div>
        <div class="clear"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="label">11-12 Actual:</div>
        <div id="value11_12" class="value"></div>
        <div class="clear"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="label">12-13 Budget:</div>
        <div id="value12_13" class="value"></div>
        <div class="clear"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="label">Change:</div>
        <div id="value_change" class="value"></div>
        <div class="clear"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="label">Description:</div>
        <div id="item_description" class="value description"></div>
        <div class="clear"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="label">Source:</div>
        <div id="item_source" class="value source"></div>
        <div class="clear"></div>
      </div>

    </div>

  </div>
  <div id="footer">Want to use this data for your own purposes? Be our guest! Check out the <%= link_to "json export","data.json" %>, or <%= link_to "download your own .csv", 'budget_data.csv' %>.<br/>TheOpenBudget was developed for GovHack 2012, and built by a team from <%= link_to "Prosple","http://www.prosple.com.au" %> and <%= link_to "OzDocsOnline", "http://www.ozdocsonline.com.au" %>. Questions, comments, complaints? <%= mail_to "robertdapice@gmail.com", "Hit us up" %>.</div>
</div>
<%= javascript_include_tag "chart" %>

<script>
  $("button").click(function(){
    $(this).addClass("active").siblings().removeClass("active");
  });
</script>